dct_description_sm: door sijn Dr. Hoocheyt Frederick Hendrick van Nassou pr. van Orangien etc.
Bar scale on map; statement reads: Vierhondert Roeden de tweeduysent makeneen Duytse Myle.
Index of place names near center of map, beneath 't Sas van Gendt.
Imprint to left of title: Visscher Excudit.
Depicts siege of Sas van Gendt in Zeeland; shows land dvisions, waterways, fortifications, infantry, horsemen.
Extensive descriptive text on sheet below map.
